			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original" xml:lang="yi">
					<pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540317_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאַלינאַ</placeName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">קרײַז סווענציאַני</placeName>)</p>
					<p>דאָ האָט זיך גיפֿונען אַן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508" type="subject">אַרבעט-לאַגער</term> פֿון דער <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-433">אָרגאַניזאַציע דאָט</orgName> (אדער <orgName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-433">טאָט</orgName> ) פֿון אַפּריל מאָנאַט 1942 ביז דעם 30-טן מאַרט 1943[.] די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">אַרבעט</term> איז באַשטאַנען [אין] האַקן וואַלד בײַ <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאַלינאַ</placeName> און אויך אויף דער אײַזנבאַן-ליניע. אין 42-טן יאָר האָבן געאַרבעט אַ 150 מאַן פֿון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">ווילנע</placeName> און פֿון <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/621713/smarhon.html">סמאָרגאָן</placeName> און <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/630515/ashmyany.html">אָסמיאַני</placeName>. ענדע 42-טן יאָר זײַנען אַ גרויסער טייל <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292"
							type="subject">קראַנק</term> געוואָרן אויף <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-493" type="subject">טיפֿוס</term>. עס האָט זיך אײַנגעגעבן די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-493" type="subject">קראַנקע</term> איבערצופֿירן
						אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">סווענציאַנער</placeName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">געטאָ</term> און זיי זענען שוין צוריק ניט געקומען. אויף זייער אָרט האָט מען אַרײַנגעשיקט אַרבעטער פֿון די שטעטלעך <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/620191/vidzy.html">ווידזי</placeName>,
							<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/628869/druysk.html">דרוּיסק</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/564792/dubina.html">דובינע</placeName>.</p>
					<p>די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">דײַטשן</term> זײַנען ניט געווען שלעכט צו די ייּדישע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבעטער</term> ,איבערהויפּט האָט זיך אויסגעצייכנט דער <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">לאַגער-פֿירער</term> , אַ לייטענאַנט פֿון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3099434/gdansk.html">דאַנציג</placeName> (זײַן נאָמען האָב איך פֿאַרגעסן). ער פֿלעגט [ד]ערלויבן די ייּדן צו גיין בעטלען אין
						די דערפֿער און אויך צו <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">אַרבעטן</term> בײַ די קריסטן אַ 3-4 טעג אין חודש, נאָר קיינער זאָל ניט זאָגן אַז ער האט זיי אָפּגעלאָזן.</p>
					<p>ענדע מאַרט 43-טן האָט מען אַלע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבעטער</term> געמוזט אָפּשיקן איו <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103">סווענציאַן אין געטאָ</placeName>. די <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבעטער</term> האָבן געוויינט ווען זיי האָבן זיך מיט די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">דײַטשן</term> געזעגנט. דער לייטענאַנט און אויך 2 פֿון די <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">וואַכלײַט</term> האָבן געוויינט. פֿון די אַלע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבעטער</term> זײַנען נאָר 2 לעבן פֿאַרבליבן - איינער פֿון <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/620191/vidzy.html">ווידז</placeName>, <persName ref="#ehri_et_tvaretsky_leib">לייב טוואָרעצקי</persName> און אַ <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">מיידל</term> פון <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/628869/druysk.html">דרוּיסק</placeName>, <persName ref="#ehri_et_feygin_sheyne">שיינע פֿייגין</persName>. זיי דאַרפֿן זיך געפֿינען אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">דײַטשלאַנד</placeName>.</p>
					<p>אין יאָר 1945 האָב איך בײַ אַ <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-763" type="subject">קריסטין</term> אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאַלינאַ</placeName> געפֿונען אַ <term
							ref="ttps://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-701" type="subject">פֿאָטאָבילד</term> פֿון אַ גרופּע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבעטער</term> פֿון <placeName
							ref="ttps://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-1529" type="camp">איגנאַלינער לאַגער</placeName>. דאָס <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-701" type="subject">בילד</term> האָב איך אָפּגעגעבן אין <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/3093133/lodz.html">לאָדזש</placeName> אין היסטאָרישן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-705" type="subject">מוזיי</term> דעם ה' <persName ref="#ehri_et_kaczerginski_sherke">ש. קאַטשערגינסקי</persName>.</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2867714/munich.html">מינכען</placeName>, דעם 7/VII 46 <persName ref="#ehri_et_korb_yerachmiel">ירחמיאל קאָרב</persName> פֿון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאַלינאַ</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">קרײַז סווענציאַני</placeName> ,<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">ווילנער</placeName> געגנט</p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
					<pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540317_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">Švenčionys district</placeName>). A <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508" type="subject">work
							camp</term> of the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-433">organization Dat</orgName> (or <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-433">Todt</orgName>) was located there from the month of <date when="1942-04">April
							1942</date> until <date when="1943-03-30">March 30, 1943</date>. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term> was comprised of chopping [wood in the] forest near <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName> and also [working] on the railway line. In the year <date when="1942">1942</date>, around 150 people from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">Vilna</placeName> as well as
							<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/621713/smarhon.html">Smarhoń</placeName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/621713/smarhon.html">Smorgon</placeName>) and <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/630515/ashmyany.html">Ashmyana</placeName> (<placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/630515/ashmyany.html">Oshmene</placeName>) worked there. At the end of <date when="1942">1942</date>, a great number became <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">sick</term> with <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-493" type="subject">typhus</term>, they succeeded in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-521" type="subject">transporting</term> the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-493" type="subject">sick</term> to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName> to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject"
							>ghetto</term> and they never returned. In their stead workers were sent from the shtetls of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/620191/vidzy.html">Vidzy</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/628869/druysk.html">Druysk</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/564792/dubina.html">Dubina</placeName>.</p>
					<p>The <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">Germans</term> did not treat the Jewish <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> badly, most of all the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477"
							type="subject">camp director</term>, a lieutenant form <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3099434/gdansk.html">Danzig</placeName> (I have forgotten his name), distinguished himself. He would allow the Jews to go begging in the villages and to <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term> for Christians three to four days per month, but no one should say that he had allowed them to do so.</p>
					<p>At the end of <date when="1943-03">March 1943</date>, all the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> had to be sent to the <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto">ghetto
							in Švenčionys</placeName>. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> cried when they parted with the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">Germans</term>. The lieutenant and another two of the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">watchmen</term> cried. Of all the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> only two remain alive, one from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/620191/vidzy.html">Vidzy</placeName>, <persName ref="#ehri_et_tvaretsky_leib">Leib Tvaretsky</persName>, and a young <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">woman</term> from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/628869/druysk.html">Dryusk</placeName>, <persName ref="#ehri_et_feygin_sheyne">Sheyne Feygin</persName>. They must be in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">Germany</placeName>,</p>
					<p>In the year <date when="1945">1945</date>, I found in the home of a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-763" type="subject">Christian</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName> a <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-701" type="subject">photograph</term> of a group of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> from the <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-1529" type="camp">Ignalina camp</placeName>. I gave the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-701" type="subject">photo</term> to the Historical <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-705" type="subject">Museum</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3093133/lodz.html">Lodz</placeName>, to Mr. <persName ref="#ehri_et_kaczerginski_sherke">Sh. Kaczerginski</persName>.</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2867714/munich.html">Munich</placeName>, <date when="1946-07-07">7/7/46</date>
						<persName ref="#ehri_et_korb_yerachmiel">Yerachmiel Korb</persName> from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">Švenčionys district</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">Vilna</placeName> region</p>
				</div>
